      <h1 class='title'>Remploy</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 21 July 2004 vol 424 cc54-5WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_54ws' title='Col. 54WS &mdash; HC Deb 21 July 2004 vol 424 c54WS' name='column_54ws' href='#column_54ws' rel='bookmark'>54WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040721_CWS_39'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-maria-eagle' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040721_CWS_39' title='Link to this speech by Ms Maria Eagle' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-maria-eagle" title="Ms Maria Eagle">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Maria Eagle)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Remploy's achievement against its targets set by Government for 2003&#x2013;04 is in the table.<table>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Target</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Achievement</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Gross margin&#x2014;the Company will achieve gross margin of &#x00A3;55 million.</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;55million</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;54.4 million</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Progressions from Remploy factories and interwork to
          open employment</td>
          <td>1,650</td>
          <td>1,408</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Average cost of a supported employee</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;10,400</td>
          <td>&#x00A3;11,095</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>Employee development time</td>
          <td>5 per cent.</td>
          <td>7.8 per cent.</td>
          </tr>
          </table></p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_55ws' title='Col. 55WS &mdash; HC Deb 21 July 2004 vol 424 c55WS' name='column_55ws' href='#column_55ws' rel='bookmark'>55WS</a><p>Remploy will publish its annual report and accounts in the autumn giving further detail of its performance throughout 2003&#x2013;04. Copies of the annual report and accounts will be placed in the Library.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
